<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Reminder - Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .payment-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .payment-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .amount {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .due-date {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffd700;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            color: #d63031;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Reminder</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name || 'there' %>,</h2>

            <p>This is a friendly reminder that your Engagematic subscription payment is coming up soon.</p>

            <div class="payment-box">
                <h3>Payment Due</h3>
                <div class="amount"><%= amount || 'â‚¹649' %>/<%= billingPeriod || 'month' %></div>
                <div class="due-date">Due: <%= dueDate || 'In 3 days' %></div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Why This Matters</h3>
                <p>To ensure uninterrupted access to all Engagematic features, please update your payment method or confirm your subscription renewal before the due date.</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What happens if payment fails?</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Your subscription will be paused</li>
                <li>You'll lose access to premium features</li>
                <li>Your content history will be preserved</li>
                <li>You can reactivate anytime by updating payment</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= paymentUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    Update Payment Method
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you've already paid, please ignore this email. If you have any questions, reply to this email and we'll help you right away.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for being a valued Engagematic member!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

